{{Han compound|衣|复|c1=s|c2=p|t1=clothes|t2=to return|ls=psc}} – lined garment.

===Etymology===
Cognate with {{och-l|復|to return; again}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). See there for more.

{{och-l|覆|id=4|to turn over; to overturn}} is an aspiration causative/iterative form of {{och-l|複|id=2}}, hence literally "to make something double over".

